name: Detention Block Rescue
description: Available exclusively at Star Wars Celebration Orlando held between April 13 and 16, 2017. While the event was promoted as being in honor of the 40th anniversary of Star Wars: A New Hope (aka Episode IV) and the upcoming release of Star Wars: The Last Jedi (aka Episode VIII), this set is strictly marketed with references to the 40th anniversary celebrations.Purchase was only available on-site at the Orange County Convention Center in Orlando, Florida, United States by winners of a daily raffle draw for $40. Approximately 500 sets were available via this raffle on each of the event's four days. Additionally, one set was awarded free each day as the prize for re-tweeting the event's giveaway announcement. Select other sets were available to invited individuals - it is unclear as to the exact number of these sets and if these sets were sold or awarded for free. A grand total of less than 2,500 sets are believed to have been produced.Each of these sets were hand-packed in a resealable plastic bag inserted into a hard cardboard slipcover-style box. Each box was sealed with an individually numbered sticker applied around the bottom edge of the box.

name: Malaysia: Bunga Raya
description: Available as a gift with purchases exceeding RM200 for the first 150 sets available upon launch at the "Cities of Wonder" event held at the Pavilion KL in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia on May 27, 2017. Subsequently, the set was available as a gift with purchases exceeding RM300 from Toys R Us outlets at Mid Valley Megamall, Pavilion KL, 1 Utama, KLCC, 101 City Mall and Empire Subang in Malaysia between May 28 and June 2, 2017.Also available at retail locations at LEGOLAND Malaysia Resort beginning July 8, 2017.The depicted Malaysian national flower is better known in the western world as a hibiscus.

name: Malaysia: Ketupat
description: Available as a gift with purchases exceeding RM200 for the first 150 sets available upon launch at the LEGO Certified Store (The Curve) in Malaysia on June 17, 2017. Subsequently, the set was available as a gift with purchases exceeding RM300 from Lego Certified Stores at Pavilion KL, The Curve, Village, Setia City Mall, 101 City Mall and Empire Subang in Malaysia between June 18 and June 23, 2017.Also available at retail locations at LEGOLAND Malaysia Resort beginning June 17, 2017.This set was also re-issued as a gift with purchases exceeding RM249.90 from LEGO Certified Stores in Malaysia beginning May 17, 2018 in honor of Hari Raya.Ketupat is a rice dumpling wrapped and woven in strips of palm leaf.

name: Malaysia: Rumah Kampung
description: Available as a gift with purchases exceeding RM200 for the first 150 sets available upon launch at Toys R Us (Mid Valley Megamall) in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia on June 3, 2017. Subsequently, the set was available as a gift with purchases exceeding RM300 from Toys R Us outlets at Mid Valley Megamall, Pavilion KL, 1 Utama, KLCC, 101 City Mall and Empire Subang and the "Cities of Wonder" event in the Pavilion KL in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia between June 4 and June 9, 2017.Also available at retail locations at LEGOLAND Malaysia Resort beginning June 24, 2017.The Rumah Kampung is a traditional village home in rural Malaysia. The building instructions refer structure as a "Kampung House".N.B.: This set has also been seen with the set number 6218684. There are no known differences between the versions.

name: Malaysia: Wau
description: Available as a gift with purchases exceeding RM200 for the first 150 sets available upon launch at the "Cities of Wonder" event held at the Pavilion KL in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia on June 10, 2017. Subsequently, the set was available as a gift with purchases exceeding RM300 from LEGO Certified Stores at Pavilion KL, The Curve, Bangsar Village, Setia City Mall, 101 City Mall and Empire Subang in Malaysia between June 11 and June 16, 2017.Also available at retail locations at LEGOLAND Malaysia Resort beginning July 1, 2017.This set was also re-issued as a gift with purchases exceeding RM249.90 from LEGO Certified Stores in Malaysia beginning May 17, 2018 in honor of Hari Raya.The Wau is a Malaysian kite often decorated with shapes of crescent moons and other colorful motifs.

name: Medic's Car

name: King Kahuka

name: M&T Dog
description:
Also known as “Micro Dog”.Available during the following promotions in celebration of Lunar (Chinese) New Year:
Gift with purchase of any LEGO product (excluding minifigures) during an experience event held between January 22 and February 4, 2018 in Singapore’s City Square Mall
Buildable during the same event as part of a family “speed build” competition held on January 27 and January 28, 2018 with winners receiving various gifts
Free for participants in a building activity held between January 25 and February 4, 2018 at Taoyuan Zhongli Dajiang International Shopping Center in Taiwan
Free for participants in a building activity held on February 3 and February 4, 2018 at Banqiao Dayuanbai in Taiwan
Free for participants in a building activity held on February 10 and February 11, 2018 at Hsinchu Giant City in Taiwan
Free for participants in a building activity held between February 14 and February 25, 2018 at Dazhi Miramar Shopping Center in Taiwan
A total of 10,000 sets were available across all four Taiwan events. The quantity of sets available at the Singapore events remains unknown. The building instructions, with the identifier 6238218, show how to assemble two variations and provide inspirational images of six other designs.

name: Easy Build Building Happening Dog
description: Available as the "lucky draw" prize for five weekly raffles conducted in Singapore during Lunar New Year celebrations between January 22 and February 25, 2018. Entry into the raffles required submission of receipt information by Singapore residents via SMS concerning purchases exceeding S$100 of LEGO products from participating retailers. Nine winners were randomly selected from each week’s submissions for a total of 45 sets available as part of this promotion.The parts were provided in a large plastic bag sealed with a twist tie. The bag was labeled with a sticker identifying the set number.The build is 30.72cm tall x 25.8cm deep x 19.2cm wide and contains “522 2x4 bricks + a few special parts”.

name: Cannon Battle
description: Some sets have the heads of the minifigs witched. V1 is the version as found in the set image. V2 is the alternate version.

name: LEGO House 6 Bricks
description: This bag is given at the exit of the LEGO House in Billund, Denmark.

name: Fortuna Temple Pavilion and Puppy

name: Lion Dance

There is no known distinction between the limited edition and general release versions.

name: Harry Potter Mosaic

With a minimum purchase of SGD$649, guests received both this set and set 6268522-1.The set was provided as a loose 48x48 stud baseplate and a single, large plastic bag filled with the 2,304 needed 1x1 plates (plus spares) sealed with tape and labeled with a large sticker identifying the set number.

name: Hermione Granger Mosaic

The set was provided as a gift for purchases exceeding CN¥699 (approximately $100). While the sets are unnumbered, distribution was limited to 5,000 sets.Hand packaged in zippered bag.Three similarly designed BrickHeadz exist with variations in leg coloring and city notation on the shirt. For the Amsterdam version, see set 6315025-1.For the Beijing version, see set 6278983-1.For the Cologne version, see set 6302766-1.

name: Christmas Heart

name: Imperial Flagship with Free Storage Case

A total of 10 sets were available as part of this promotion.The parts were provided in a large plastic bag sealed with a twist tie. The bag was labeled with a sticker identifying the set number. The instructions were spiral bound and scans are available hereThe build is 27cm tall.

name: Micro Piglet

An inbound or outbound ticket to/from the airport was required to access this location.Building instructions and further information can be found from Brick Hello here.

The building instructions (courtesy of LEGO-KEI) are likewise printed on two double-sided sheets of paper similar to that used for similar events. However, these two items are then placed into a cardboard box similar to most sets.

name: Panda

name: Cologne Brickheadz
description: No BrickHeadz range number assigned.Available exclusively at the LEGO Pop-Up Shop at the Comic-Con Experience (CCXP) held in Cologne, Germany between June 27 and June 30, 2019. The set was provided as a gift for purchases exceeding €75.While the sets are unnumbered, distribution was limited to 250 sets per day (1000 total sets for the event).Hand packaged in zippered bag.The "I ❤️ Cologne" sticker was produced due to production timing concerns with making a printed brick. The sticker is slightly too large for the intended brick.Three similarly designed BrickHeadz exist with variations in leg coloring and city notation on the shirt. For the Amsterdam version, see set 6315025-1.For the Beijing version, see set 6278983-1.For the Shanghai version, see set 6270050-1.

This part bag and the instructions are then presented in an open-fronted cardboard box.Three similarly designed BrickHeadz exist with variations in leg coloring and city notation on the shirt. For the Beijing version, see set 6278983-1.For the Cologne version, see set 6302766-1.For the Shanghai version, see set 6270050-1.

name: Tantive IV

Available as a gift during various promotions including:
May 4, 2019: In-store “make and take” build at LEGO Brand Stores as part of “May the 4th” celebrations
November 2, 2019: In-store “make and take” build at Toys R Us locations in Canada

The set number is only known to exist on the pre-packaged versions used for the November 26, 2021 event. This version came in a zippered bag with the same printed build instructions as seen at the earlier events.

name: Public Works Center
description: Available in Europe and North America only.

name: Stuttgart Brand Store Opening Associate Figure
description: Available exclusively as a gift with purchase during Grand Opening celebrations for the LEGO Store in Stuttgart, Germany held on August 4, 2021. The store opened in April 2021 but celebrations were delayed due to COVID-19 pandemic restrictions. While the sets are unnumbered, distribution was limited to customers making  purchases of 75€ or more. Exact production numbers are unknown but was likely 250 similar to other LEGO Brand Store Opening Associate Figure sets. Parts are packaged in a clear plastic bag with a resealable flap. This part bag and the instructions are then presented in an open-fronted cardboard box.

name: New York 5th Avenue Brand Store Opening Associate Figure
description: Available exclusively as a gift with purchase during Grand Opening celebrations for the LEGO Store on 5th Avenue in New York City, New York, USA on June 27, 2021. Unlike other Brand Store Opening Associate Figures, features the apron commonly worn by LEGO Brand Store associates in the United States. While the sets are unnumbered, distribution was limited to customers making purchases of $75 or more. Exact production numbers are unknown but was likely 250 similar to other LEGO Brand Store Opening Associate Figure sets. Parts are packaged in a clear plastic bag with a resealable flap. name: Trophy
description:
Small set handed out in the Copenhagen Lego Store. Came packed in a "service bag" and the instructions printed on a sheet of A4 paper.Also available at “make and take” events held in the LEGO Brand Store in Utrecht, The Netherlands on October 9, October 15, October 16, October 22 and October 23, 2022 as part of celebration of the newest season of that country’s edition of the LEGO Masters TV show.This set, under the number 6385436, was also available during a series of “make and take” events held in the United States promoting the City Stuntz subtheme. This version contained identical parts but the building instructions were printed on US letter size paper. Known events included:
The LEGO Brand Store in Water Tower Place, Chicago, Illinois on October 8 and October 9, 2022
The LEGO Brand Store Flatiron in New York City, New York on October 22 and October 23, 2022
The flagship LEGO Brand Store on 5th Avenue in New York City, New York on October 22 and October 23, 2022
All events were while supplies lasted and limited to one set per person.

name: Golden Snitch
description:
Available as a “make and take” gift during various promotions including:
Canada: Indigo and Chapters bookstores on October 13, 2018 in advance of the launch of the Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald movie and the movie’s associated sets
United States: Select Barnes and Noble locations on July 13, 2019 promoting the early-release availability of 2019 Harry Potter sets
United Kingdom: LEGO Brand Stores on September 18, September 19, September 25 and September 26, 2011 honoring the 20th anniversary of the Wizarding World of Harry Potter theme
During the Canada and United States events, participants selected loose parts from containers and the building instructions were on printed pages available for review (and to take at some locations). During the United Kingdom events, the set’s parts were pre-sorted into zippered plastic bags and included folded, printed building instructions with both the bag and instructions bearing the set number. The actual building steps and part inventories are identical across all the events.

name: Extra-Large Gift Set (ABB)
description: WARNING - Work in progress. We are in the process of updating the inventories for this set, and some parts might show up seemingly with a wrong color. Also, the inventories are not yet complete or confirmed. Apologies for the inconvenience.This is one of the three sets (together with 700.2-1 and 700.3-1) that started the LEGO history in 1949.This original Automatic Binding Bricks (ABB) version was released in Denmark in 1949 and in Sweden in 1950. This is a five-color version with slotted bricks, doors and windows, and two additional art cards (not inventoried).In 1951 the number of 2x2 slotted bricks is reduced, and a green thin 10x20 baseplate is added (set 700.1-2).In 1952 the number of colors is reduced to 4 as the blue slotted bricks disappeared (set 700.1-3).In 1953 the slotted Automatic Binding Bricks were replaced by hollow Mursten bricks (set 700.1-4).

name: Single 2 x 4 Brick (ABB)
description: WARNING - Work in progress. We are in the process of updating the inventories for this set, and so the number and type of parts might change in the future. Some parts might also show up seemingly with a wrong color, as we are adding new colors for these parts. Apologies for the inconvenience.After disappointing sales in 1949, LEGO started to sell their individual bricks, doors and windows through their Danish vendors. In 1950 the assortment consisted of 2x2 (700.2.1-1) and 2x4 (700.1.1-1) bricks (both single and double slotted); 1x4x2 (700.B.1-1), 1x2x3 (700.B.2-1) and 1x2x2 (700.B.3-1) windows without glass; and a 1x2x4 (700.B.4-1) door without glass; in at least five different colors. These sets were only available in Denmark.The different inventories represent the commonly available colors for single slotted bricks:    v1 ABB Blue    v2 ABB Green    v3 ABB Red    v4 ABB White    v5 ABB YellowAs LEGO was experimenting with colors in this period, there are many examples of bricks in other colors, as well as many different marbled bricks. Presumably, these were manufactured in minor quantities, and are, as yet, considered anomalies. (image to follow)

name: Extra-Large Gift Set (Mursten)
description: 700.1-2WARNING - Work in progress. We are in the process of updating the inventories for this set, and some parts might show up seemingly with a wrong color. Also, the inventories are not yet complete or confirmed. Apologies for the inconvenience.In 1953 the hollow Mursten bricks replaced the slotted Automatic Binding Bricks used in set 700.1-1.The first inventory (v1 - 1953 version) represents the original Mursten version. This is a five-color version with hollow bricks, both slotted windows and doors and classic windows and doors with glass and a 10 x 20 green used as baseplate.In 1954 the number colors is reduced to 2, red and white, which is represented in the second inventory (v2 - 1954 version).In 1956 slotted windows and doors were discontinued and only classic windows and doors with glass remained (v3 1956 version).In 1957 the hollow Mursten bricks were replaced by System bricks with tubes, in 700.1-3.

name: Movie Maker
description: Make your own movie with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70820 LEGO Movie Maker building toy, featuring a movie stage, camera stand for your smartphone device and plenty of cool action props! The stage features a frame with sliding, adjustable arms at the top to hold and animate props, characters and accessory elements, a double-sided backdrop with alternative scenes, plus a platform with built-in sliders to move characters around. Attach the camera stand to any of the 3 special points on the stage for different angles and camera panning movements. This THE LEGO MOVIE 2 set also comes with action props like Emmet’s Escape Buggy and Rex’s Rexplorer, 3 minifigures, a mini-doll figure, 4 brick-built figures and a raptor figure for creative play. Movie stage measures over 9” (25cm) high, 6” (16cm) wide and 11” (28cm) deep.Camera stand measures over 5” (14cm) high, 5” (15cm) wide and 2” (6cm) deep.Escape Buggy measures over 1” (5cm) high, 1” (4cm) long and 1” (4cm) wide.Rex’s Rexplorer measures over 1” (4cm) high, 2” (7cm) long and 2” (6cm) wide.Alien invader stands over 3” (10cm) tall.(From LEGO.com)

name: Emmet and Benny's 'Build and Fix' Workshop!
description: Give your youngster a stellar master-building experience with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70821 Emmet and Benny’s ‘Build and Fix’ Workshop! This LEGO 4+ safe learning set is specially designed to be fun and easy for preschoolers and youngsters, and features LEGO Benny's Spaceship with a minifigure cockpit, foldout boosters and removable space buggy, and Emmet's Escape Buggy, plus a special Starter Brick base that lets even first-time builders experience the pride of constructing buildings, vehicles and more, all on their own. The included simple guide to build and play will also help your young master builder understand the purpose of the building instructions and expand their imagination and confidence for the perfect start to LEGO brick building. This simple LEGO astronaut toy includes 2 minifigures, a buildable gas station and a tool trolley with lots of assorted tool elements for endless play possibilities. Benny’s Spaceship toy measures over 1” (5cm) high, 6” (16cm) long and 3” (9cm) wide.Emmet’s Escape Buggy toy car measures over 1” (4cm) high, 5” (15cm) long and 2” (6cm) wide.Gas station measures over 2” (6cm) high, 2” (6cm) wide and 1” (3cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)This is one of four sets which piloted LEGO Audio and Braille Building Instructions during 2019. These building instructions can be found here.

name: Unikitty's Sweetest Friends EVER!
description: Enjoy a drink and a snack with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70822 Unikitty’s Sweetest Friends EVER! This fun kids’ toy building set features 3 buildable THE LEGO MOVIE 2 figures—Unikitty, Ice Cream Cone and Chocolate Bar—plus a tea trolley with teapot, coffee cup and cake accessory elements for creative play. (From LEGO.com)

name: Emmet's Thricycle!
description: Raise your master-building ability to another level with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70823 Emmet’s Thricycle! This awesome construction toy features a minifigure seat, 3 vertically stacked rubber tires and foldout stabilizers. It includes a fuel station with a buildable gas pump, catapult function and parking spot for the Thricycle, plus THE LEGO MOVIE 2 characters—an Emmet minifigure and a brick-built alien invader with a chomping mouth and rotating cyclops eye. Emmet’s Thricycle construction vehicle toy measures over 6” (16cm) high, 2” (7cm) long and 1” (3cm) wide.Fuel station measures over 2” (7cm) high, 4” (11cm) wide and 3” (9cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: Introducing Queen Watevra Wa'Nabi
description: Join Lucy and meet the shape-shifting Queen Watevra Wa’Nabi for the first time with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70824 Introducing Queen Watevra Wa’Nabi toy building set. This fun-packed building toy features a brick-built Queen Watevra Wa’Nabi in horse form with a rotating platform, plus 4 interchangeable face expression decorations for when you rebuild the shape-shifting queen into pile-of-bricks form. This THE LEGO MOVIE 2 set also includes a buildable Banarnar character, Sweet Mayhem and Susan mini-dolls, and a Lucy minifigure. Queen Watevra Wa’Nabi horse with platform measures over 4” (11cm) high, 3” (9cm) long and 2” (6cm) wide.Banarnar stands over 1” (3cm) tall.(From LEGO.com)

name: Queen Watevra's Build Whatever Box!
description: Build and rebuild THE LEGO MOVIE 2 character Queen Watevra Wa’Nabi in 15 different forms with 70825 Queen Watevra’s Build Whatever Box! This creative builder set has instructions to build each version of the shape-shifting queen, from a grumpy volcano to a happy butterfly or colorful rocket. This versatile building toy also comes with inspirational ideas for young master builders to create their own shapes. Queen Watevra Wa’Nabi in pile-of-bricks form measures over 4” (11cm) high, 2” (7cm) wide and under 1” (1cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: Rex's Rex-treme Offroader!
description: Display your master-building versatility when you rebuild the 3-in-1 THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70826 Rex’s Rex-treme Offroader and Recon Rex-o-saurus into the Rex-o-saurus Quad or Execu-Rex-o-saurus. The offroader seats 2 minifigures and has a rotating rear turret with 2 stud shooters, while the Recon Rex-o-saurus features snapping jaws, posable legs, 2 stud shooters and a buildable removable gun (non-shooting) that can also be used as a minifigure weapon. This awesome playset includes 2 minifigures and a buildable Plantimal figure to recreate action-packed scenes from THE LEGO MOVIE 2. Rex's Rex-treme Offroader measures over 2” (6cm) high, 5” (14cm) long and 2” (7cm) wide.Recon Rex-o-saurus measures over 3” (10cm) high, 5” (13cm) long and 1” (5cm) wide.Rex-o-saurus Quad measures over 3” (8cm) high, 5” (14cm) long and 2” (7cm) wide.Execu-Rex-o-saurus measures over 2” (7cm) high, 5” (13cm) long and 3” (9cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Ultrakatty & Warrior Lucy!
description: Ride into battle against the alien invader with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70827 Ultrakatty & Warrior Lucy! and rescue Emmet. Ultrakatty features a minifigure cockpit, a posable head which can be rebuilt for 3 different facial expressions, and a posable tail and legs. This awesome building toy includes Lucy and Emmet minifigures, plus a brick-built alien invader with a chomping mouth and rotating eye, to recreate action-packed scenes from THE LEGO MOVIE 2. Ultrakatty measures over 3” (8cm) high, 8” (21cm) long and 3” (8cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Pop-Up Party Bus
description: All aboard THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70828 Pop-Up Party Bus and party on with Disco Kitty and friends. This fun toy bus features an opening cockpit for the Zebe figure, opening roof and sides for easy play, foldout loudspeakers, a LEGO light brick to light up the rotating dancefloor and a flip-up disco ball with translucent-colored elements. This THE LEGO MOVIE 2 set includes buildable Unikitty as Disco Kitty and Zebe figures, plus Tempo and Melody mini-doll figures. Pop-Up Party Bus measures over 9” (24cm) high, 11” (30cm) long and 9” (23cm) wide.Zebe stands over 3” (8cm) tall.(From LEGO.com)

name: Emmet and Lucy's Escape Buggy!
description: Drive away from danger in THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70829 Emmet and Lucy’s Escape Buggy, featuring seats for 2 minifigures, opening doors and hood, foldout arrow gun (non-shooting) and suspension. This fun-packed construction toy also includes a buildable base with an explode function, 3 minifigures and 3 buildable figures—MetalBeard, Star and Heart—with cool weapons and accessory elements. Escape Buggy measures over 5” (15cm) high, 8” (22cm) long and 5” (13cm) wide.Buildable base measures over 3” (8cm) high, 1” (5cm) wide and 2” (6cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: Sweet Mayhem's Systar Starship!
description: Help Emmet and Lucy evade capture by THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70830 Sweet Mayhem’s Systar Starship toy, featuring an opening cockpit for a mini-doll or minifigure, retractable landing gear, disc shooter, a roll of stickers and an opening prison cell. This fun construction toy includes 2 minifigures, a mini-doll figure and buildable Star and Heart toy figures to role-play action from THE LEGO MOVIE 2. Measures over 5” (14cm) high, 6” (16cm) long and 11” (28cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)Replacement sticker rolls are available as a separate set 5005738-1.

name: Emmet's Dream House / Rescue Rocket!
description: Show you are a master rebuilder with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70831 Emmet’s Dream House/Rescue Rocket! This 2-in-1 construction toy features Emmet’s home which can be rebuilt into a rocket. The house toy opens out for easy interior play and has a detailed living room/kitchen and attic. Remove the roof and use parts from the water tower and barricade to create a rocket with spring-loaded shooters and adjustable engines. This fun building toy includes 3 minifigures, plus buildable Planty and Unikitty as Warrior Kitty figures with weapons and accessories to role-play action from THE LEGO MOVIE 2. Dream House measures over 5” (14cm) high, 5” (13cm) wide and 5” (13cm) deep.Toy rocket measures over 5” (15cm) high, 7” (20cm) long and 7” (18cm) wide.Water tower measures over 5” (15cm) high, 6” (17cm) wide and 2” (7cm) deep.Barricade measures over 1” (3cm) high, 6” (16cm) wide and 2” (6cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: Emmet’s Builder Box!
description: Open up a world of master-building adventures with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70832 Emmet’s Builder Box, featuring 3 buildable models—Emmet’s digger vehicle, house and construction mech. The digger has an adjustable front bucket to lift rubble elements, the mini-build house features an opening door and the rotating construction mech has a minifigure cockpit, 4 posable arms and 2 demolition balls. This LEGO building toy includes an Emmet minifigure and a brick-built alien invader for endless role-play fun. Digger vehicle measures over 3” (8cm) high, 4” (12cm) long and 1” (5cm) wide.House toy measures over 3” (10cm) high, 2” (6cm) wide and 2” (6cm) deep.Construction mech measures over 4” (11cm) high, 1” (5cm) long and 5” (15cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Lucy’s Builder Box!
description: Give your young master builder hours of fun with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70833 Lucy’s Builder Box! This creative toy features 3 buildable models— Lucy’s motorcycle with a ramp, a rotating dance stage and the Unikitty spa with spa bath and washstand. This simple LEGO toy building set also includes a Lucy minifigure and a brick-built Unikitty figure for endless role-play fun. Toy motorcycle measures over 1” (4cm) high and 2” (7cm) long.Dance stage measures over 3” (10cm) high, 2” (6cm) wide and 2” (6cm) deep.Unikitty spa measures over 3” (9cm) high, 3” (10cm) wide and 2” (7cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: MetalBeard's Heavy Metal Motor Trike!
description: Power into battle against Sweet Mayhem and Star with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70834 MetalBeard’s Heavy Metal Motor Trike! It features a built-in MetalBeard minifigure head, rotating turret with adjustable shooting cannons, adjustable shark shooter with snapping jaws, crow's nest and flag and a huge front wheel. This fun-packed construction toy includes an Apocalypse-borg Benny minifigure and a Sweet Mayhem mini-doll figure with cool weapons and accessories, plus a brick-built Star figure to recreate action-packed adventures from THE LEGO MOVIE 2. Measures over 6” (17cm) high, 12” (31cm) long and 7” (19cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Rex's Rexplorer!
description: Team up with Rex, Emmet and the raptors against the Plantimals with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70835 Rex’s Rexplorer space toy set! The Rexplorer features 2 opening cockpits, spring-loaded and stud shooters, rotating engines, an opening rear compartment for interior play, and a removable speeder. This popular and fun spaceship toy also includes 2 minifigures, 2 THE LEGO MOVIE 2 raptor figures with a brick-built mountable stud shooter and raptor skateboard, plus 2 brick-built Plantimals (including one with a trap function). Rex's Rexplorer building toy measures over 7” (18cm) high, 12” (33cm) long and 7” (19cm) wide.Plantimal 1 measures over 3” (8cm) high, 8” (21cm) wide and 2” (7cm) deep.Plantimal 2 measures over 1” (4cm) high, 2” (6cm) wide and 2” (6cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: Battle-Ready Batman and MetalBeard
description: Scuttle into action against Star with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70836 Battle-Ready Batman and MetalBeard. This action-packed Batman playset features LEGO MOVIE pirate MetalBeard in crab mech form, with a built-in LEGO MetalBeard minifigure head, opening treasure chest with MetalBeard's internal organ elements, flip-down crow's nest with a flag and posable legs, plus a Batman throne with an adjustable ‘You're Welcome' sign. This THE LEGO MOVIE 2 pirate toy also includes 2 minifigures, a brick-built Star figure, and weapons and accessories.Batman throne measures 5” (14cm) high, 3” (9cm) wide and 1” (5cm) deep.MetalBeard crab mech measures 6” (16cm) high, 4” (11cm) long and 4” (12cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Welcome to Apocalypseburg!
description: Enjoy an epic 360-degree play experience—and prepare for an alien invasion—with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70840 Welcome to Apocalypseburg! construction toy. An advanced building set, it has over 3,000 pieces and presents an awesome challenge even for master builders. This THE LEGO MOVIE 2 set features a section of the Statue of Liberty with a chill-out room in the head, café, Scribble Cop’s office with a chair-kicking function, armory, barber’s/tattoo parlor, Lucy’s hideout, Fuse’s workshop, rooftop diner, gym, spa, lookout platforms and loads more! This action-packed toy also comes with 12 THE LEGO MOVIE 2 minifigures to role-play and reimagine your favorite scenes from the blockbuster film.This creative toy includes 12 new-for-January-2019 THE LEGO MOVIE 2 minifigures: Emmet, Lucy, Batman, Scribble Cop, Harley Quinn, Green Lantern, ’Where are my pants?’ Guy, Larry the Barista, Chainsaw Dave, Mo-Hawk, Roxxi and Fuse, plus a rat figure.This new-for-January-2019 toy measures over 20” (52cm) high, 19” (49cm) wide and 12” (33cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: Benny's Space Squad
description: Join forces with THE LEGO MOVIE 2 70841 Benny’s Space Squad for fun adventures in outer space. This action-packed building set features a spaceship toy with a minifigure seat and a lunar buggy with 2 minifigure seats. Role-play scenes from THE LEGO MOVIE 2 with this space toy for kids including 4 LEGO astronaut minifigures with assorted accessories. Spaceship toy measures over 1” (4cm) high, 3” (9cm) long and 1” (5cm) wide.Lunar buggy measures over 1” (3cm) high, 1” (5cm) long and 1” (3cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Adventures with Mario Starter Course
description:
LEGO Audio & Braille instructions can be found here.This set has been found in two different packaging designs:
The triangular shaped box, available since 2020, is the more common version and appeared at multiple retailers.
The rectangular box version, available since 2021, is currently only known to have been available from Costco. The boxart includes images of both Mario and Luigi (Luigi is not included in the set).
The set inventories are identical between both designs.A bundle including this set was available in a VIP Sweepstakes from March 10 through 13, 2022, for 50 VIP points per entry.Not all sets come with a spare 75c16.

name: Propeller Mario Power-Up Pack
description: This outfit fits on the LEGO Mario figure in the Adventures with Mario Starter Course (71360-1) toy playset. When LEGO Mario wears this buildable toy accessory and is lifted up, listen for the sound of propellers and when Mario is launched into the air, players can earn extra digital coins to boost their score.(From LEGO.com)

name: Cat Mario Power-Up Pack
description: This brick-built accessory fits on the LEGO Mario figure that is included in the Adventures with Mario Starter Course (71360) toy playset, causing unique sounds and a unique image to appear on Mario’s torso screen.The LEGO Mario figure meows and purrs when he wears the cat costume. He also gains the special ability to walk up vertical obstacles and collect digital coins to boost the player’s score.(From LEGO.com)

name: Builder Mario Power-Up Pack
description: The buildable costume fits on the LEGO Mario figure that is included in the Adventures with Mario Starter Course (71360-1) toy playset to boost the in-game possibilities.When LEGO Mario (figure not included) is wearing this outfit, a player can earn digital coins by making him stomp hard on LEGO bricks in the course they have created.

name: Nintendo Entertainment System
description: Set can be optionally paired with the LEGO Mario from set 71360-1 by placing Mario in a purpose-built slot on top of the television. Once paired, LEGO Mario reacts to the on-screen enemies, obstacles and power-ups just like in the Super Mario Bros. game.

name: Western Train
description: "The 1970's are regarded by many LEGO fans as an outstanding decade for LEGO trains and the Western Train from 1976 is seen as a vintage model. Based on the design of classic 19th century locomotives, the engine included details such as a smokestack, water boiler and move-able drive shafts. The set included two carriages, three identical cowboy figures and a single black horse built from LEGO bricks. It is believed that this model was the inspiration for the Western locomotives that appeared in the LEGOLAND Park shortly after."-- from the employee gift re-creation (set 4002016-1-s2) building instructions

Updated boxart depicts the new design and part count while some of the individual set images still reflect the older design.For the original design, see set 75090-2N.B.: Some sets may include the international version of the sticker sheet despite this re-design's primary sale in North American markets. The set inventory includes the much more common North American version of the sticker sheet.

The boxart and set images on this page reflect the original set design.For the redesigned version, see set 75090-1N.B.: Some sets may include the North American version of the sticker sheet. The set inventory includes the International version of the sticker sheet.

This was reflected in the replacement of a minifigure head (part 3626cpr2762 replaces part 3626cpr2388) and a helmet (part 33648pr0224 replaces part 33648pr0001). This version is listed as 75188-2.The second version was only sold in North America (United States and Canada) due to the retirement of this set in Europe prior to the minifigure change. Updated packaging and building instructions reflect the change.

name: Resistance Bomber (Finch Dallow version)

This was reflected in the replacement of a minifigure head (part 3626cpr2762 replaces part 3626cpr2388) and a helmet (part 33648pr0224 replaces part 33648pr0001).The second version was only sold in North America (United States and Canada) due to the retirement of this set in Europe prior to the minifigure change. Updated packaging and building instructions reflect the change.

name: Naboo Starfighter Microfighter
description: Get set for fun-sized battles with the LEGO Star Wars 75223 Naboo Starfighter Microfighter. Part of the LEGO Microfighters Series 6 collection, this mini-sized version of Anakin Skywalker’s favorite starship has lots of authentic details, plus 2 flick missiles, R2-D2's dome and space for the young Skywalker pilot minifigure with his wrench.Series 6 LEGO Microfighters building toy measures over 1” (3cm) high, 4” (11cm) long and 2” (7cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Sith Infiltrator Microfighter
description: Give the gift of endless fun with the LEGO Star Wars 75224 Sith Infiltrator Microfighter. This Series 6 building toy version of Darth Maul’s spacecraft features stud shooters and space for the Sith Lord minifigure on top. The set also comes with a double-bladed Lightsaber for even more LEGO Star Wars creative play.LEGO Star Wars ship measures over 1” (4cm) high, 3” (9cm) long and 2” (7cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Elite Praetorian Guard Battle Pack
description: Let any LEGO builder play out fun-filled training drills with the LEGO Star Wars 75225 Elite Praetorian Guard Battle Pack. This starter pack set features a training platform with spinning turntables for 2 minifigures to stand on to replicate intense training duels. There's also a weapon rack with detachable weapons, a training droid for even more creative play, 3 Elite Praetorian Guards and a First Order Stormtrooper. Training platform measures over 4” (11cm) wide and 2” (7cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: Inferno Squad Battle Pack
description: Add iconic Star Wars characters to your collection with the LEGO Star Wars 75226 Inferno Squad Battle Pack. Featuring a TIE fighter style speeder with stud shooters and space for a minifigure, plus 3 Inferno Squad Agents and brave heroine Iden Versio, any fan will love to expand their LEGO Star Wars universe with this collectible construction toy.Speeder building toy measures over 1” (4cm) high, 4” (11cm) long and 3” (9cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Darth Vader Bust
description: Available for purchase by raffle winning attendees of Star Wars Celebration Chicago held at McCormick Place in Chicago, Illinois, USA between April 11 and April 15, 2019 for $39.99. To obtain a purchase opportunity, attendees were required to win an online raffle. This raffle opened on March 26, 2019 and was selected at various intervals until the start of the event. Additionally, in keeping with a recent LEGO decision to minimize exclusive release of sets, the set was also available for purchase in the United States from Target for the same price. This purchase was restricted to Target Red Card holders. While originally announced as being available on April 11, 2019, release was delayed and didn't begin until April 12, 2019. After a rapid initial sellout, the set was made available at various points in April and May 2019 as stock was replenished.Unlike previous years, this set was not individually numbered.Dimensions: 10.32" (262mm) x 2.32" (59mm) x 11.1" (282mm)

name: Escape Pod vs. Dewback Microfighters
description: Play out epic LEGO brick adventures with the LEGO Star Wars 75228 Escape Pod vs. Dewback Microfighters dual pack building toy. This set features an escape pod with big engine detailing and space for the C-3PO and R2-D2 building toy LEGO figures, while the buildable Dewback creature has a posable head and tail, clips for attaching weapons and space on top to sit the Sandtrooper. And with separate building instructions for each model, Star Wars fans will love sharing the building experience with their friends and family. Dewback measures over 1” (4cm) high, 4” (12cm) long and 1” (5cm) wide.Escape pod measures over 1” (4cm) high, 3” (8cm) long and 1” (4cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Death Star Escape
description: Immerse any Star Wars fan in an unforgettable space adventure with the LEGO Star Wars 75229 Death Star Escape set. Recreating the epic scene from Star Wars: A New Hope featuring Luke Skywalker and Princess Leia, this great set includes a hinged Death Star setting with an entrance, lever-activated closing door and retracting walkway, plus a second section with a platform, access ladder, hidden Mouse Droid and an opening box with electrobinoculars. Fans will love to attach Leia to Luke's back, help him grab the grappling hook and swing over the chasm to safety away from the Stormtrooper. Includes 3 minifigures and a Mouse Droid LEGO figure. Death Star scene building toy (folded out) measures over 5” (15cm) high, 6” (16cm) wide and 3” (8cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: Kylo Ren & Sith Trooper
description: Kylo Ren: BrickHeadz range #94Sith Trooper: BrickHeadz range #95

name: Droid Gunship
description: Reinforce any LEGO® Star Wars construction toy collector’s forces with the heavily armored LEGO Star Wars 75233 Droid Gunship. As seen in Star Wars: The Revenge of the Sith, this detailed model features an opening cockpit with space for a Kashyyyk Battle Droid LEGO figure, lowering landing gear and non-firing directional cannons at the front. Add no less than 8 flick missiles and 2 stud shooters, plus Chief Tarfful and Yoda minifigures to the mix, and you have the perfect recipe for a galaxy of action-packed LEGO Star Wars adventures! This building toy includes 2 minifigures and 2 LEGO figures. Droid Gunship construction toy measures over 1” (5cm) high, 11” (29cm) long and 9” (24cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: AT-AP Walker
description: Add some heavy firepower to any LEGO fan’s collection with the tough LEGO Star Wars 75234 AT-AP Walker. This impressive model features articulated legs and a retractable third leg, plus an opening top and sides that reveal a detailed 2-minifigure cockpit. The model also includes a rotating and elevating top turret with a seat for a minifigure and a spring-loaded shooter for exciting battling action. With Chewbacca, Clone Commander Gree and Kashyyyk Clone Trooper minifigures plus 2 Kashyyyk Battle Droid LEGO figures, this collectible construction toy makes for a great birthday gift for kids.Imperial walker Star Wars building toy measures over 9” (24cm) high, 11” (29cm) long and 5” (15cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: X-Wing Starfighter Trench Run
description: Let your child play out unforgettable LEGO Star Wars space adventures with the 75235 X-Wing Starfighter Trench Run collectible building toy. This LEGO 4+ set is designed to be fun and easy for youngsters, with folding wings and an opening minifigure cockpit, plus a special Starter Brick base that lets even first-time builders experience the pride of constructing buildings, vehicles and more, all on their own. The included simple guide to build and play will also help your young Rebel warrior understand the purpose of the building steps and grow their imagination and confidence for the perfect start to LEGO brick building in a familiar Star Wars setting. This simple LEGO set also includes a rotating turret for endless action play as well as Luke Skywalker and Stormtrooper minifigures, plus an R2-D2 Star Wars LEGO droid figure. X-wing LEGO® Star Wars construction toy measures over 3” (9cm) high, 5” (15cm) long and 7” (18cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: TIE Fighter Attack
description: Give your young Imperial pilot the perfect introduction to LEGO Star Wars starship battles with this 75237 TIE Fighter Attack set. With an opening cockpit with space inside for the TIE Fighter Pilot minifigure and special Starter Bricks that let even first-time builders experience the pride of constructing the model, all on their own, LEGO 4+ safe learning sets are specially designed to be fun and easy for preschoolers and youngsters. This TIE Fighter also includes a small Rebel command station and Rebel Fleet Trooper minifigure for endless play fun, while the included simple guide to build and play will also help youngsters understand the purpose of the building steps and grow their imagination and confidence for the perfect start to LEGO brick building in an inspiring Star Wars setting. TIE Fighter LEGO Star Wars ship measures over 5” (14cm) high, 4” (11cm) long and 4” (12cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Rebel A-Wing Starfighter
description: Immerse your youngster in exciting LEGO Star Wars adventures with the 75247 Rebel A-Wing Starfighter collectible building toy. This LEGO 4+ safe learning set is specially designed to be fun and easy for preschoolers and youngsters, featuring rotating blasters and an opening cockpit and space for the A-wing Pilot, plus an easy-build Starter Brick base that lets even first-time builders experience the pride of constructing the craft, all on their own. This construction toy also includes a service station mini build to keep the A-wing ready for action, plus marshaling paddles for friendly droid C-3PO to guide it off on another Rebel mission! The included simple guide to build and play will also help your youngster understand the purpose of the building steps and grow their imagination and confidence for the perfect start to LEGO brick building in an instantly recognizable Star Wars world. Includes 2 minifigures. A-wing LEGO Star Wars ship measures over 2” (6cm) high, 5” (13cm) long and 4” (11cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: A-Wing Starfighter
description: Information from LEGO parts replacement indicate there should be 2x copies of the 69882 (EID 6318649) sheet in each set along with 1x of the 67750 (EID 6299663) sheet. Early release versions of the set in North America incorrectly included only one of each sheet (this problem does not appear to have occurred in Europe), but replacements are available from LEGO Customer Service. However, only one of each sheet is needed to construct the set.  A note in the instruction book indicates that the second sheet is a practice sheet for the canopy.

name: Mos Eisley Cantina
description: According to Bricks&Pieces on LEGO.com, this set comes with a Light Bluish Grey 3069bpr0307. But both the Building Instructions and physical conformation states the set has a Dark Bluish Grey 3069bpr0090 instead. Maybe there will be an update in later releases when the stock of the 3069bpr0090 runs out? Please let us know if you find a 3069bpr0307 in your copy of the set.

name: The Razor Crest
description: Due to copyright issues, the set got renamed to The Mandalorian Bounty Hunter Transport at the last moment, as The Razor Crest was already trademarked by a company in Germany. It seems that later on the name was changed back.

name: Bespin Duel
description: Originally designed for 2020 Star Wars Celebration Anaheim.Following the cancellation of that event due to the COVID-19 pandemic, the set was made available for public purchase on August 27, 2020 - the originally announced start date of the in-person event via LEGO.com and Target (United States) and Toys R Us (Canada). Sales were exclusive to the United States and Canada and purchase limits were imposed on all retail channels. The Target offering required the use of a Target Red Card as a further means of purchase limit control.

description: The Child: BrickHeadz range #113The Mandalorian: BrickHeadz range #114

name: Snowtrooper Battle Pack
description: In addition to retail sales, available as part of a gift with purchase bundle from LEGO Certified Stores in South Africa. The bundle required purchase of set 75313-1 and included as gifts this set along with sets 40539-1, 40557-1, 40558-1 and 853946-1.

description: While planned for a 2020 release, this set's release has been postponed due to the COVID-19 pandemic delaying the release of the Minions: The Rise of Gru movie until June 2022.

name: Brick-Built Minions and Their Lair
description: The set contains the parts to build two of the three Minion lairs at one time. Instructions are provided to rebuild Kevin's lair into Bob's lair. Stuart's lair is unaffected by this rebuild.Kevin's lair measures over 3" (9cm) long, 4" (11cm) wide and over 5" (15cm) tallStuart's lair measures over 3" (9cm) long, 4" (11cm) wide and 5" (14cm tall)Bob's lair measures over 3" (9cm) long, 4" (11cm) wide and 4" (12cm) tall

name: Neytiri & Thanator vs. AMP Suit Quaritch
Firehouse Headquarters
description: Based on the 1984 version of the movie.Designed to provide parking inside for the LEGO Ideas Ecto-1 set 21108-1.

name: Ecto-1 & 2
description: Based on the 2016 version of the movie.A smaller scale version of the 2016 Ecto-1 can be found in the LEGO Dimensions set 71242-1.For versions of Ecto-1 based on the 1984 film, see set 21108-1 for a large scale LEGO Ideas version and set 71228-1 for a smaller scale LEGO Dimensions version.For a version of Ecto-1 based on the 2021 film, see set 10274-1.N.B.: The torso and head designs for the Jillian Holtzmann minifig are correctly included in the inventory. However, the set image displayed is based on official LEGO artwork used on the packaging and incorrectly uses other torsos and heads from the set.

name: Chevrolet Corvette Z06
description: Hit top speed with this buildable, minifigure-scale LEGO Speed Champions version of a true American icon - the Chevrolet Corvette Z06. The set includes interchangeable wheel trims, racing helmet, wrench and a television camera element, to fire the imagination of budding motor racing fans. Includes a Chevrolet Racing driver minifigure.(From LEGO.com)

name: Ford Mustang GT
description: Power across the desert with this buildable, minifigure-scale LEGO Speed Champions version of the American muscle car famous for its V8 engine - the Ford Mustang GT. Play out different race-day scenarios with this set that features interchangeable wheel trims, a wrench and a timing-board element. Includes a Ford racing driver minifigure.(From LEGO.com)

name: Audi R18 e-tron quattro
description: Fuel racing dreams with this LEGO Speed Champions version of one of the most successful track cars of all time. This buildable, minifigure-scale version of the Audi R18 e-tron quattro comes with interchangeable wheel trims, wrench and a fuel pump element. Includes an Audi racing driver minifigure.(From LEGO.com)

name: Audi R8 LMS ultra
description: Role-play a GT-class track race with this buildable, minifigure-scale LEGO Speed Champions Audi R8 LMS. Choose the wheel trims and check the car with the wrench, then put on the driver's helmet and race away. Celebrate victory by lifting the trophy on the podium. Includes an Audi racing driver minifigure.(From LEGO.com)

name: Chevrolet Camaro Drag Race
description: Green is for go in this drag racing set featuring LEGO Speed Champions versions of the iconic 1969 and 2016 Chevrolet Camaro cars and a functioning start/finish line. Switch the ‘lights' from red to green to begin the race. With 2 Chevrolet Racing driver minifigures plus a race official with the checkered flag and a trophy for the winner, there's everything needed to role-play a classic vs. modern drag strip racing event. Includes 3 minifigures: 2 Chevrolet Racing drivers and a race official.(From LEGO.com)This set inventory is complete. The number of parts is greater than shown on the box. LEGO element id 6107391 consists of 8 parts, but is listed as 1 in the instruction inventory.

name: Ford F-150 Raptor & Ford Model A Hot Rod
description: Experience a classic Hot Rod race day with this multifunctional set. The Ford F-150 Raptor comes with suspension and a trailer to transport the Model A Hot Rod to the race. Prepare the Model A in the team garage, which comes fully equipped with engine crane, welding machine and an oil can, and turn it around to reveal a victory podium and trophy to celebrate victory. Includes 4 minifigures: a Hot Rod racing driver, racing driver, mechanic and a race official.(From LEGO.com)

name: Porsche 919 Hybrid and 917K Pit Lane
description: Play out your own action-packed race day with the Porsche team, matching the vintage Porsche 917K against the modern 919 Hybrid. Prepare for the race with the car lift and assorted tools in the dual-purpose garage. Then fold out fully to create a pit stop and monitor the race for the checkered flag. Includes 5 minifigures: a vintage Porsche racing driver, modern Porsche racing driver, 2 mechanics and a race official.(From LEGO.com)There are currently differences between Rebrickable and BrickLink for the spare parts:54200 White - Bags 2, 5, and 6 have 1 spare each. BL shows only 2.54200 Black - Bag 2 has a spare. BL shows none.2780 Black - Bags 4, 5, and 6 have 1 spare each. BL shows only 2.18979a 4 Flat Silver - BL includes these in regular inventory. They are shown in the picture, so to have a complete set, BL Sellers must include them. Because they are not actually used in building the model, Rebrickable considers them spares.

name: Mercedes-AMG GT3
description: Show your skills as both an engineer and driver with this buildable LEGO Speed Champions version of the Mercedes-AMG GT3. Customizable for race or road-driving modes, it features wheels with rubber tires, yellow rims and black trims, a removable front splitter, adjustable and removable rear wing, removable windshield and authentic racing colors and race-graphics stickers. Includes a minifigure.(From LEGO.com)

name: Bugatti Chiron
description: Gear up for quad-turbocharged action with this buildable LEGO Speed Champions version of one of the world’s most exclusive hyper cars—the Bugatti Chiron. This vehicle features wheels with rubber tires, a removable windshield plus iconic and realistic details. Test your driving skills with the three included marker cones. Includes a minifigure.(From LEGO.com)

name: Scuderia Ferrari SF16-H
description: Power to victory with this buildable LEGO Speed Champions version of the Scuderia Ferrari SF16-H race car, featuring wheels with rubber tires and two interchangeable race numbers so you can pretend to be different Scuderia Ferrari drivers. The set also includes a pit wall with start-finish-line, pit monitor element and checkered flag with waving function, plus wrench and walkie-talkie elements to maximize the role-play fun. Includes a minifigure.(From LEGO.com)

name: McLaren 720S
description: Become a supercar designer and racing driver with the buildable LEGO Speed Champions version of the McLaren 720S plus design studio. This buildable car features loads of authentic details and comes with a design desk and play-starting elements, including an original design sketch and printed 3D miniature version of the McLaren 720S. Also includes one minifigure.(From LEGO.com)

name: 2016 Ford GT & 1966 Ford GT40
description: Get set for a historic race with LEGO Speed Champions versions of the stunning 2016 Ford GT and 1966 Ford GT40 endurance cars. Each car features space for a racing driver minifigure, wheels with rubber tires, removable windshields and iconic details. With a race marshal minifigure plus a victory podium with a gold-colored trophy and checkered flag element, there’s everything needed to role-play a modern vs. classic 24-hour race. Includes three minifigures.(From LEGO.com)

name: Ferrari FXX K & Development Center
description: Push the boundaries of technological innovation at the development center with the LEGO Speed Champions version of the Ferrari FXX K. This set features a wind tunnel with a functioning roller and a rotating turbine for the included buildable, minifigure-scale Ferrari FXX K car. A test lab with play-starting accessory elements, including a design board, computer monitors, 3D car model and a design sketch of the FXX K, will also fire the imagination of budding motor racing engineers and drivers. Includes four minifigures.(From LEGO.com)

name: MERCEDES AMG PETRONAS Formula One Team
description: Role-play an entire race day with the MERCEDES AMG PETRONAS Formula One Team with this richly detailed LEGO Speed Champions set, featuring 2 buildable Mercedes F1 W07 Hybrid cars. Packed with play-starting features and functions, it includes a fully equipped pit garage with car jack function, and a pit wall with monitor, checkered flag and translucent start-finish light-style elements. Dial up the big-race atmosphere with the TV camera rig with an adjustable camera arm, plus a grandstand with big screen and rotate function to reveal the winner’s podium. Includes eight minifigures.(From LEGO.com)An identically designed version of the number 44 car is the available in set 75995-1

name: 1968 Ford Mustang Fastback
description: Create a buildable LEGO version of a classic American muscle car - the LEGO Speed Champions 75884 1968 Ford Mustang Fastback. Ideal for display or racing, it features a minifigure cockpit, removable windshield, wheels with rubber tires and gold-colored rims, and authentic design details. This building set includes a minifigure and buildable 'timing' board to play out race scenarios.(From LEGO.com)

name: Ford Fiesta M-Sport WRC
description: Display and race a buildable LEGO Speed Champions 75885 Fiesta M-Sport WRC, featuring a minifigure cockpit, removable windshield, 2 interchangeable hoods—including one with spotlight-style elements to play out low-light/nighttime racing scenarios, and authentic design details. This buildable set includes a minifigure. (From LEGO.com)

name: Ferrari 488 GT3 "Scuderia Corsa"
description: Create a buildable LEGO version of the super fast car that won the 2016 IMSA SportsCar series - the LEGO Speed Champions 75886 Ferrari 488 GT3 "Scuderia Corsa", featuring a minifigure cockpit, removable windshield and authentic design details. This construction toy includes a minifigure and trophy to play out race scenarios.(From LEGO.com)

name: Porsche 919 Hybrid
description: Create a buildable LEGO Speed Champions 75887 Porsche 919 Hybrid endurance racing car, featuring a minifigure cockpit, removable windshield and authentic design details. This cool toy for kids includes a minifigure, plus a start/finish post and a laptop element to play out race scenarios.(From LEGO.com)

name: Porsche 911 RSR and 911 Turbo 3.0
description: Prepare for a modern vs. classic race with LEGO Speed Champions 75888 Porsche 911 RSR and 911 Turbo 3.0 cars, featuring minifigure cockpits, removable windshields and authentic design details. This building toy includes 3 minifigures, a lap counter, pit wall with a race-position board, and checkered flag elements to play out race scenarios. (From LEGO.com)An identically built but re-colored white version of the lime Porsche 911 Turbo 3.0 can be found in set 75895-1

name: Ferrari Ultimate Garage
description: Create the LEGO Speed Champions 75889 Ferrari Ultimate Garage with a workshop/museum, attachable racetrack section and LEGO Speed Champions versions of the classic Ferrari 250 GTO, Ferrari 488 GTE and historic Ferrari 312 T4 cars. Build the cars in the workshop, featuring an adjustable car ramp, vintage-style fuel pump and a tool rack, display a car in the museum, and race around the curbs and under the arch on the racetrack section. This building set includes 7 minifigures for endless role-play options.(From LEGO.com)

name: Ferrari F40 Competizione
description: Build, race and display the LEGO Speed Champions 75890 Ferrari F40 Competizione toy car, then transform it into the classic F40 road car, the last car that Enzo Ferrari oversaw in his lifetime! Packed with authentic details, this 2-in-1 model features a minifigure cockpit with a removable windshield, plus interchangeable hoods and spoilers to turn the Competizione into the road version of the F40. This car toy also includes a Ferrari racing driver minifigure to play out exciting race scenarios.Ferrari F40 Competizione car for kids measures over 1” (4cm) high, 5” (13cm) long and 1” (5cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: Chevrolet Camaro ZL1 Race Car
description: Race for victory with the LEGO Speed Champions 75891 Chevrolet Camaro ZL1 Race Car toy, featuring a minifigure cockpit with an adjustable roll cage, removable windshield and wheels with Chevrolet Camaro-branded rims. This cool stock car racing toy comes with a Chevy Camaro racing driver minifigure and a fuel canister element to play out racing and pit-stop scenarios. Measures over 1” (4cm) high, 5” (14cm) long and 1” (5cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: McLaren Senna
description: Drive on the edge with the LEGO Speed Champions 75892 McLaren Senna model car toy! This cool LEGO version of the road car inspired by the late, great and legendarily daring racing driver Ayrton Senna features a minifigure cockpit, removable windshield, interchangeable rims, and McLaren and Senna logo stickers. This super toy car for kids comes with a buildable wind tunnel with rotating fan and a McLaren racing driver minifigure to play out car development and fast car racing scenarios. McLaren Senna toy car measures over 1” (4cm) high, 5” (15cm) long and 1” (5cm) wide.Wind tunnel measures over 1” (5cm) high, 2” (6cm) wide and 1” (4cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: 2018 Dodge Challenger SRT Demon and 1970 Dodge Charger R/T
description: LEGO reports 478 pieces for this set.Enjoy a thrilling building and drag racing experience for kids and adults with this awesome LEGO Speed Champions 75893 2018 Dodge Challenger SRT Demon and 1970 Dodge Charger R/T toy car playset! The Dodge Challenger features 2 sets of wheel rims, authentic design details and decorative stickers while the cool LEGO version of the Dodge Charger, an iconic American muscle car, has a removable supercharger and alternate engine cover. Get the car racing action going with a buildable Christmas tree start light, plus a race marshal with a checkered flag and 2 driver minifigures. 2018 Dodge Challenger SRT Demon measures over 1” (4cm) high, 5” (14cm) long and 2” (6cm) wide.1970 Dodge Charger R/T muscle car measures over 1” (4cm) high, 5” (15cm) long and 1” (5cm) wide.Christmas tree start light measures over 4” (11cm) high, 1” (4cm) wide and 1” (3cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)

name: 1967 Mini Cooper S Rally and 2018 MINI John Cooper Works Buggy
description: Stage a classic vs. modern rally race with these cool LEGO Speed Champions 75894 1967 Mini Cooper S Rally and 2018 MINI John Cooper Works Buggy car toys! The 1967 Mini Cooper S Rally features a roof rack with 2 spare tires, just like the original car, while the 2018 MINI John Cooper Works Buggy has suspension to drive over rough terrain. Play out exciting rally racing scenarios with 4 LEGO minifigures and a fully equipped pit stop station, including a buildable car jack stand, a mechanic's creeper, tool racks, assorted tools and computer screen elements.1967 Mini Cooper S Rally toy car for kids measures over 2” (6cm) high, 3” (9cm) long and 1” (4cm) wide.2018 MINI John Cooper Works Buggy measures over 2” (7cm) high, 5” (13cm) long and 2” (7cm) wide.Pit stop station measures over 5” (13cm) high, 11” (30cm) wide and 4” (12cm) deep. (From LEGO.com)

name: 1974 Porsche 911 Turbo 3.0
description: Re-colored release of one vehicle included in set 75888-1

name: LaFerrari
description: Gear up and take the super-stylish LEGO Speed Champions version of LaFerrari for a spin! This race-ready, buildable vehicle features all the cool details of Ferrari’s iconic hybrid sports car. Check the removable wheels with the wrench and attach the unique wheel trims. Then jump in the driver’s seat, wait at the starting lights and accelerate away! Includes a driver minifigure with assorted accessories.(From LEGO.com)

name: Woody and Buzz to the Rescue
description: Available in two different box styles - one white and one blue. There is no distinction in the inventory between the two styles.

name: 458 Italia GT2
description: Rev up for glory with the LEGO Speed Champions version of the super-fast 458 Italia GT2! This race-ready, buildable vehicle boasts all the real-life details of Ferrari’s streamlined racing car. Attach the cool, unique wheel trims and place the driver at the steering wheel. Compete against your friends in LEGO® Speed Champions races for the silver trophy! Includes a driver minifigure with assorted accessories.(From LEGO.com)

name: McLaren P1
description: Hit top speed in the LEGO Speed Champions version of the super-powerful McLaren P1! This race-ready, buildable vehicle has all the authentic details of McLaren’s ultimate hybrid supercar. Attach the stylish wheel trims and use the wrench to prep your car. Put on the driver’s helmet and get set to speed away. Weave around the cones–and make sure you stay inside the curb. Test your skills in thrilling LEGO Speed Champions races against your friends! Includes a driver minifigure with assorted accessories.(From LEGO.com)

name: Porsche 918 Spyder
description: Go for a thrilling drive with the LEGO Speed Champions version of the Porsche 918 Spyder! This race-ready, buildable vehicle boasts all the real-life details of Porsche’s awesome hybrid sports car. Select from 2 sets of cool wheel trims and use the wrench to make adjustments. Then place the driver at the steering wheel and accelerate away. Take on your friends’ LEGO Speed Champions cars in a race to be first past the checkered flag! Includes a driver minifigure with assorted accessories.(From LEGO.com)

name: McLaren Mercedes Pit Stop
description: Prep your McLaren Mercedes MP4-29 race car for action with this awesome multi-function LEGO Speed Champions play set. Join the pit crew in the hi-tech garage to work on the car with a complete set of tools, 3-screen computer console and more. Swap the nose of the car, place the driver in the cockpit and activate the launch function to power out of the garage. Fold out the garage walls to create a life-like pit stop setting with a fuel pump and movable wheel guns. But don’t delay too long in thepits–you’ll have to be super-fast to beat your friends’ LEGO Speed Champions cars to win the golden trophy! Includes 3 minifigures with assorted accessories: a driver, male pit crew member and a female pit crew member.(From LEGO.com)

name: Porsche 911 GT Finish Line
description: Race against your friends and claim a place on the podium with this exciting LEGO Speed Champions play set. Prep the 2 powerful, Porsche 911 GT race cars with the tools in the mini-garage. Attach the unique Porsche 911 wheel trims to make your car look super-sleek and then drive to the start-finish line. Activate the dropping start lights and it’s red, amber, green for go! Capture all the action with the camerawoman as you race to be first past the checkered flag. Then climb up to the podium for the prize-giving ceremony. Accept your trophy and stand proudly as the national flags are raised! Includes 4 minifigures with assorted accessories: 2 Porsche drivers, a camerawoman and a race marshal.(From LEGO.com)

name: F14 T & Scuderia Ferrari Truck
description: Drive the Scuderia Ferrari team and F14 T race car to the circuit in the fully-equipped Scuderia Ferrari truck. Open up the roof of the cabin to place the truck driver at the steering wheel with a team crew member alongside. Detach the trailer and turn the lever to release the standing feet. Fold out the roof and sides to access the awesome race car, scooter and array of cool equipment including a complete tool set and computer screens. Lower the rear hatch and activate the launch function to push the F14 T down the ramp. Then challenge your friends and their LEGO Speed Champions cars to thrilling races! Includes 6 minifigures with assorted accessories: a driver, team truck driver and 4 team crew members.(From LEGO.com)

name: Dilophosaurus Outpost Attack
description: While released at the same time as many sets related to Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom, this set depicts no scene seen in that or any other Jurassic World franchise movie or TV show. The smaller dinosaur has been referred to in various materials alternately as either an unnamed baby dilophosaurus or as the named velociraptor, Blue.

name: Triceratops Rampage
description:
Youngsters will love creating exciting dinosaur action adventures with this LEGO Jurassic World 75937 Triceratops Rampage building set. The colorful playset includes an Egg Spinner ride with 3 dinosaur-egg seats for minifigures and a spinning function, plus a gate and waiting area for the ride. There is also a posable Triceratops toy dinosaur figure, a collapsible fence ­and a minifigure buggy to play out a dinosaur escape and pursuit. This building toy for kids includes 4 Jurassic World minifigures to inspire creative role-play.
This LEGO® Jurassic World dinosaur toy playset includes 4 new-for-June-2019 minifigures: Owen Grady, Simon Masrani, Allison Miles and a tourist.
Egg Spinner ride measures over 4” (12cm) high, 4” (12cm) wide and 7” (19cm) deep.
Entrance gate measures over 3” (10cm) high, 5” (14cm) wide and 1” (4cm) deep.
Triceratops LEGO® dinosaur figure measures over 3” (8cm) high, 7” (19cm) long and 2” (6cm) wide.
Dinosaur fences measures over 3” (10cm) high, 9” (25cm) wide and 1” (5cm) deep.
Buggy measures over 1” (3cm) high, 2” (6cm) long and 1” (4cm) wide.
(From Lego.com)

Hogwarts Clock Tower

name: Hanzo vs. Genji
description: Now your favorite Overwatch fan can build the Hanamura dojo in LEGO bricks with LEGO Overwatch 75971 Hanzo vs. Genji. Based on the internationally acclaimed team-based action game, this Overwatch toy recreates the epic face-off for the Hanamura dojo between the rival dragon brothers Hanzo and cyborg ninja Genji. With weapons for the highly recognizable Overwatch heroes and a buildable dojo, kids will love to play out the action from the game, while older fans will want to show off the set next to their gaming setup.Hanamura dojo building toy measures over 4” (11cm) high, 8” (22cm) wide and 3” (9cm) deep. (From LEGO.com)

name: Dorado Showdown
description: Now your favorite Overwatch fan can build an iconic Dorado building and payload truck with LEGO Overwatch 75972 Dorado Showdown! Based on the internationally acclaimed team-based action game, this Overwatch building set features an instantly recognizable building from the popular Dorado map and 3 characters, Soldier: 76, Reaper and McCree. With Overwatch weapons, Dorado building, and a payload truck like in the game, fans of Overwatch will want to build and display it for their friends to see, while youngsters will like playing with the vehicle and mini market building from the game.Dorado-style building toy measures over 6” (17cm) high, 5” (15cm) wide and 1” (4cm) deep.Payload truck creative play toy measures over 3” (8cm) high, 5” (15cm) long and 3” (8cm) wide.(From LEGO.com)

name: D.Va & Reinhardt
description: For your favorite Overwatch fan, a buildable mech suit and powered armor with LEGO Overwatch 75973 D.Va & Reinhardt! Each of these instantly recognizable Overwatch tank heroes features an Overwatch minifigure so fans can place the highly-detailed Overwatch characters inside through the hatches that open. Reinhardt features a massive buildable Rocket Hammer and both minifigures have smaller weapons so younger fans can play out the action of the game, while older fans may want to display the minifigures and toys next to their gaming setup!D.Va building toy stands over 5” (15cm) tall.Reinhardt building toy stands over 5” (14cm) tall.(From LEGO.com)

name: Bastion
description: A fully reconfigurable LEGO Overwatch 75974 Bastion figure for your favorite Overwatch fan! One of the most recognizable Overwatch characters from the internationally acclaimed team-based action game, this buildable toy display model can be configured from recon mode to sentry mode without any rebuilding! Fans will love the realistic detail of this Overwatch toy and will want to display it near their gaming setup—an Overwatch collectible for every fan!Bastion building toy in recon mode stands over 10” (26cm) tall and in sentry mode stands over 6” (17cm) tall.(From LEGO.com)

name: Watchpoint: Gibraltar
description: For the Overwatch fan, the iconic Overwatch rocket and launch tower from one of the game’s most popular maps with LEGO Overwatch Watchpoint: Gibraltar 75975! Based on the internationally acclaimed team-based action game, this building set features an Overwatch rocket that splits into 2 separate rockets, and 3 Overwatch characters including Pharah with her Rocket Launcher, Mercy with her Caduceus Staff and Blaster, Reaper with his twin Hellfire Shotguns, and a Winston big figure with his Tesla Cannon. Youngsters will like playing with the buildable rocket and Overwatch heroes with their unique weapons, while adult fans will want to build and display this instantly recognizable collectible model near their gaming rigs to show their affinity for the game!Rocket building toy measures over 1” (5cm) high, 14” (37cm) long and 7” (19cm) wide with both rockets combined.Launch pad construction toy measures over 14” (37cm) high, 8” (22cm) wide, and 8” (22cm) deep.(From LEGO.com)Designed to be connected to set 75970-1.

name: Diagon Alley
description: Depicts the following locations:* Florean Fortescue's Ice Cream Parlor* Flourish & Blotts* Ollivanders Wand Shop* Quality Quidditch Supplies* Scribbulus Writing Implements* Weasley's Wizard Wheezesalong with entrances to:* The Daily Prophet* Knockturn Alley
